narration_text: A bathroom with a toilet in the middle
A room full of meters and mechanical equipment
A restaurant room filled with tables and chairs
A man sitting on his bed looking at his phone. The man gets up from the bed to pick up the TV remote and turns it on. He then sits back down on the bed.
A bathroom that has blood all over the walls, floor, sink, and shower. There is an axe in a puddle of blood.
A wooden room where multiple pigeons fly to and from perches on the far wall.

In a dark room, a door opens and a person with a hazmat suit is standing in another room. The person then walks through the door and walks toward a button on the right wall and presses it. Another door begins to open.
A winter/spring forest landscape with lots of trees with no leaves, moving in the wind.
An ambulance and firetruck back into fire station's garage doors.

A soccer game is being played between a yellow and an orange team. A foul is whistled against the yellow team as a yellow and orange player collide. The orange team receives the ball and kicks it toward the yellow goalie.
On a roof that is under construction during a windy, grey day. One hears machines being used in the background.
A person is spray painting graffiti on an abandoned building
In an underground tunnel where a biker peddles towards the camera and one can see people walking.
At a dance competition where a dance team is preforming in front of a large audience. Music is blaring and colourful lights fill the stage.

Under a dark bridge. A biker rides by and a woman runs out from under the bridge immediately screaming as a person grabs her. The woman begins to laugh and the two people walk/run away still intertwined with each other.
A male in a hoodie walks toward the camera and puts on a mask. The male then hides behind a tree.  A woman runs by and is tackled/grabbed by the male. The male pulls her behind the tree.
A go kart track where a group of people are racing in go karts.
In what looks like a medical facility. A women in scrubs walks towards freezer doors, opens one up and pulls a large gurney out of the freezer a little bit and then walks away.
A group of paramedics bring in a person on a gurney into a hospital.
An eye doctor is completing an eye exam on a client.
In a hospital, in a far room people are moving another person around. There are lots of staff waling around the hospital floor.
A woman is walking outside the hospital doors and begins to cough frequently.
Outside a European church people walk by it.
In a dance studio, a woman is completing a dance routine.
Three horses are standing outside in a fenced off portion in the yard, connected to what seems to be a barn.
At the base of a water slide, people in tubes finish taking the slide and walk off with their tubes.
At a male stripper show. There is loud music and colourful lights. The men are preforming in front of a large audience who cheer loudly when the men rip their shirts off.
A crowd of people are sitting and standing around a ledge that overlooks a city. Music is playing, some people are drinking and smoking.
Outside a tropical house people walk around it.
A woman walks to an area to feed 4 small animals that look to be cats or small dogs.
A woman walks toward an area to feed 4 animals that appear to be cats or small dogs.
On a bridge over a highway. A person watches at the railings. Cars drive under and on the bridge.
5 people taking turns rock climbing on different walls. Some sit in the middle of the walls.
In a car dealership show room. Multiple cars are parked around the room.
At a party. People are dressed very nicely. People are talking while Uptown Funk plays in the background. Colourful lights fill the room.
A person on a stage teaches a large group of people on a dance floor how to dance. They all jump in unison.
A shadowy person stands on the side of the screen staring into the camera.
A woman is getting a tattoo on her calf by an man at a tattoo shop.
On a ferris wheel, one can hear and see bits of an amusement park or carnival.
Looking at a restaurant two people are ordering food at the counter. Staff members walk behind the counter.
In a movie theatre, people walk in and around the room to go to their movie room.
In a barn, little puppies walk around, play with each other and make small noises.
Looking at and into a dark rocky tunnel
In a church, a casket sits at the front of the stage. No person sits in the chairs.
In a church, a large amount of people sit with paper in their hands as they watch a choir and their conductor sing.
In a surgical room, a person is being operated on. The doctors and nurses talk to each other.
In a grocery store a person walks down an isle, picks up a small green box, reads the box, and puts it in their basket.
In a park in a city. The grass and trees are green. Cars drive by.

Armed people in black with guns are surrounding a door down a hall. There is a loud bang and the armed people run behind a wall. The door shuts and the armed people talk loud and point their guns towards it. A person in blue, leans against another wall the entire time.
A woman is practicing shooting a gun at a virtual reality simulation with two other people. The gun makes a large bang sound.
Looking at a winter landscape with trees and open land.
People sit on rocks in a park that looks towards the tall buildings of a city.
In a basement, a man plays drums well. He is surrounded by other instruments and drum kits.
A man stands by a table loading a gun. There are a lot of guns on racks around him. He is in room that looks to be a gun shop.
At a workout class. There is a man that is on a stage teaching the small class of women. They are doing excertises with a bar over their shoulders. They do squats and lunges. Music plays.
A woman sits on a mattress, bottle feeding a baby perched up on a pillow.
On a bridge platform looking down on houses and trees in the distance. There seems to be an old building sculpture on the side of the platform.
At a train station, people with suitcases walk off and away from the train. Another train arrives at the station.
In a dark small room where two candles light the space. There seems to be movement and sounds, but one cannot see where the sounds are coming from.
During the winter a person is trying to shovel their car out of the snow. The person continuously shovels the snow and puts it somewhere behind the car.
At a kennel, a dog is locked up behind metal bars. The dog barks a lot and wags its tail.
On a sunny day at a white sand beach. Small waves crash on the shore. Some people sit under blue umbrellas.
A woman plays the piano that overlooks an open window that seeing the tops of other houses/buildings.
At a kennel, cats are in cages. They meow continuously and walk around their cage.
At a kennel, cats are in cages. They walk around their cage and meow continuously.
On a field, chickens walk around, cluck, and peck at the ground. Some fly around in the background.
Downtown on a busy street overlooking lots of very large electronic billboards. People are walking around, taking pictures. Cars drive by on the street.
At a hair salon, a male is getting his hair cut by an older man. No one else is in the salon.
In an ambulance. A person lies on a gurney. One can hear their heart beat electronically. A medic takes notes.
In a room, pigs walk and run around in their kennels.
At a miniature golf course. Neon lights fill the room. A person hits the golf ball.
A person is at an indoor gun range shooting towards a target multiple times.
A double decker red bus stops at a bus station and people walk onto the bus.
A double decker red bus stops at an outdoor bus station and a person walks onto the bus.
In a white jail cell, one sees a bed, a closet, a desk, and a toilet. A small window with metal bars is above the bed.
A yellow helicopter slowly begins to land on a field near a building.
Three men are in a bedroom continuously laughing together.

Public washroom is silent. There is no one inside. There is one toilet and a bin. The walls are made of white rectangular tiles and a blue stripe along the perimeter of the wall, on the even level. It is clean inside and bright.

Inside of a mechanical room with a lot of technical appliances. It is tan colored. There are a lot of black knobs, gages with red arrows. There is a big pipe on the celling and a helm connected to it. On the left side of the room there are stairs with three steps that lead to another room.

Inside a restaurant. Multiple chairs stand across the room, orange and grey colored. The tables are white, simple, and there are no people inside. Tables have napkins on them. The room is bright with big floor-length glass windows. Over some tables, there are chandeliers of simple design, black and circular.

Inside the apartment bedroom, that it is white and spacious. A man sits on a bed, he is looking at his phone. He places it on the nightstand shortly after and gets up from the bed. He moves towards the other table and grabs a remote from the TV. He returns to the bed and turns on the TV.

Inside of the bathroom with a shower, washing machine, toilet, and a sink. The white tiles of the walls are covered in blood. There are marks of hands on the toilet cover, walls, and the curtain of the shower. There is an axe lying on top of the washing machine next to the toilet, it is covered with red blood, it made a small puddle. Over the toilet, there is a sign painted by blood that says "RUN". There are no people inside.

Pigeonry with 7 pigeons. It is made out of wood and has some rectangular shelves inside for the birds. There are two windows, one of which is smaller. The floor is filled with a thin layer of sand, there are also a few wooden plaques laying around. Pigeons are flying up and down near the same wall. They are calm.

A corridor with light yellow walls. There is a lamp on the wall. A sturdy door slowly opens and we see a man in a yellow head to toe costume. He is wearing a gas mask and black gloves. The door slowly closes when he is already inside. He comes up to the wall with a phone on it. He touches it and starts to dial in some numbers. This while time the light of the lamp slowly flashes.
A nature scene. Bright blue sky in the winter with some hills and trees. Trees do not have any leaves anymore. The wind blows and the branches slowly rock.
Outside of the fire department station. There are two trucks going inside of the red building. The sides of the truck display a number "112". Both of the trucks are red.

It is a football match on the grass field. The weather is cold, and people who watch the match are wearing jackets. They stand near the pitch. One man sits on a chair, watching the practice. The players are wearing orange and yellow uniforms. The player with number five in an orange t-shirt standswith  the ball and gives a pass to his teammate. They continue to play.

A cityscape of a small town somewhere in Britain. The camera is positioned on top of the old building, that is being renovated and has scaffolding on the two peaks. The weather is windy and cloudy, one white car passes down the road. The private houses are mostly brown and white. The trees have a little bit of green on them.
An abandoned old building with grey garage doors. A woman paints graffiti in a bubble style on them. The windows are cracked and after she finishes, she steps back.
Somewhere underground in a tunnel with a dimmed lighting. It is empty except for a man on a bike that rides it slowly.

The scene is set inside of the concert hall. There is a large dance floor, and dancers are in the center. They are performing in the centre while strobe lights shine in the background. Lights are purple and blue. A big crowd around the dancers is cheering and watching them.

The scene is set inside of a tunnel, where a dark evening is seen. A cyclist goes inside of the tunnel. After that, a woman running from the other side appears. She is attacked by a man who drags her to the side. They dissapear in the dark.

A man approaches the camera, putting on an anonymous mask. Then he proceeds to hide behind a tree next to him. He waits while a woman in a green shirt, who is running, passes him. He drags her by the waist, while she struggles to break free. They struggle and fight, but he makes it to the tree where he was hiding with her.
Inside of a carting treck, cars are going around in circles. There are 8 drivers, who drive slowly, without bumping in anything.

Inside a morgue room, which looks very clean with white tires on the floor and warm lights. There are 3 refrigerators. A blonde woman in blue scrubs comes in through the door. She opens one of the fridges and pulls the tray with a body in a white bag halfway. It stays in that position. Then she goes away, leaving the tray out and the fridge open.

Inside of an entrance to the hospital. A group of paramedics in red and green warm suits comes in. They walk through the sliding door slowly. They have a patient lying on a rolling table, covered in blue blankets. The group of people continues to walk in to the next sliding door. They dissapear after that.

Inside of an optometrist's office, there is a doctor examining a patient's eyesight on a special machine. They sit in a corner of the office, next to the doctor's computer. The doctor is wearing a white coat, the patient is in a long-sleeve sweater. The door to the room is open to the inside, and the room's number is 14.

Inside the hospital's corridor. The walls are painted white, and there are some medical devices along the walls. The doors to one of the exam rooms is open and we see a nurse there. There is also two women passing by, a nurse who brings a woman to the exam room. The nurse, who is wearing a red jacket over her uniform, goes away once the patient is inside. Meanwhile, the patient flicks the light switch.

Outside of the hospital entrance, in the evening, a woman wearing white coat tries to put on her backpack. She struggles a lot because of the weight and her posture slouches once it is on her shoulders. She goes away.

On a square in a European city, there is a catholic church. It is white and located in old part of the town, with cobalt road. A woman passes by towards the small houses, which are yellow. Except for her, it is empty.

Inside of a dance studio, there are poles for dancing. There is a woman, standing on her arms upside down, she moves her legs slowly in a wave-like pattern. She gets down on her knees and continues to dance with her arms, sitting down. She performs a split and gets up.
Two different horses on a farm are standing near the fence. They are calm and looking around. One of the horses moves their head down to graze some grass. The weather is cloudy and gloomy.
The bottom of the aquapark slide. Some finish their slide down and try to get up with their tubing. They come out of the water in pairs, one by one.

5 men are dancing in front of a large crowd. Strobing lights flash and the men rip their white tanks off their chest. They start spinning their shirts as if they are about to throw it in the audience and point to people in the public. The dancers stop and continue to hold it above their chest.
A large number of people sit on top of the hill. They watch the sunset. People are in small groups chatting, hugging, and looking at the view.
An outside of a big old white house. There are palms in the court, the sun shines brightly and there are a lot of trees outside. There are some people exiting the house moving outside.

The scene is set in a park, on a bright day. A woman comes into frame and there are a few grey foxes following her. She stops near a fallen branch and starts feeding the animals. They come in a circle and follow the food.
(missing)

There is a busy highway, and the camera is set on top of a crossing bridge for pedestrians. There are a lot of cars going in different direction. The bridge is red, and the highway is surrounded by trees.

Inside of a climbing centre, one boulder tries to climb up a wall with an incline. He places his legs carefully. There are other people as well on the other wall. Two people also observe sitting further from the wall on the matt.
Car dealership. There are a lot of cars from volkswagen. They are shiny and stand far apart from each other.

It is inside a dark ballroom. Many people are going around, dressed in official tuxes and floor-length dresses. The ceiling is bright pink, with some blue accents. The light wooden parquet floor reflects the lights. Further in the room, there are more people in small groups. Close to the observer, there is a roulette that spins, while the croupier collects the chips and moves away, walking to the other side of the room.

Inside a concert hall, there is a performer on the stage with a microphone, dancing in front of a large crowd. The audience is dressed officially, and they mimic the moves of a man on the stage. People jump and wiggle their feet in rhythm. Disco lights strobe and play around. There is also another man who comes on stage at the end from the audience. He walks straight to the performer and takes the microphone from him.

There is an empty black scene. There are some dots of light far away and a man stands with a flashlight directed on his face from upside down. Above him, there is a big blob of yellow color and some signs inside that resemble letters, but the resolution is not that good.

Tattoo office with a man tattooing a woman's ankle. It is spacious, with another table in a corner. A tattoo master picks up a machine and moves closer to the leg, leaning in to get a closer look. The client lies there on her back, looking down to see what is going on.

Inside of a cabin of a Ferris wheel. It has bright red railings and is circular in shape. The wheel slowly spins and we can see the surroundings down on the ground with multiple cars parked and trailers. It is sunset time. We see some people walking on the ground to the merry-go-round, which shines brightly.

Middle Eastern restaurant with display cabinets and some food in them. A customer walks in and picks up their food. At the same time, there is a woman who is still looking. Close to the entrance, there are clear fridges with drinks in them. Employees are cleaning the open kitchen and preparing a kebab with meat that spins on a stick.

Movie theatre entrance with multiple posters of new films. In the centre, there is a check-out with a cashier talking to the customers. People are walking to the doors of the cinema halls. In the corner, people are walking up and down the stairs.
Inside of the room with hay and mats on the floor. 8 dark puppies are inside the room. 3 of them are playing with each other, biting and sniffing. Other puppies are asleep under the warming lamps.
Inside a dark tunnel at night. The walls are made of stone. There is one pipe going along it closer to the floor. There is only one lamp that shines on the side.

Inside of a church with a few rows of chairs. It is bright inside. Near the lectern, there is a coffin with a big pile of white flowers on top of it. There is no one inside. There is a cross on the wall, and windows have some mosaic on them.

Inside of an old catholic church, there is an orchestra giving a performance. The dirigent faces the audience with his back, meanwhile the audience is sitting on the bench. The orchestra plays following the gestures.
Surgeons are performing a procedure inside the operating room. It is really bright inside with multiple sources of light. They are wearing blue costumes, while around one table in the centre.

Inside the supermarket, there are aisles of canned goods. A woman wearing a green coat comes to the boxes with tea and stands there for some time. She picks up one and places it in her basket and goes away.
Outside, in the park somewhere in the city. The point of view is on the green grass, overlooking some tall office buildings. There are some cars parked outside of the park.

Inside the building corridor, there are armed men in black bulletproof vests and masks. They retreat to the back and point the gun at the end of the corridor. There is also another person standing against the wall, wearing blue vest. They do not take part in the whole action.
Inside the shooting range, there are two men and one woman who shoots in the target. All of them wear earmuffs. One man helps her to reload the gun, while the other stands there in the back.
Winter day in the countryside, ground covered in snow. Sun is really bright, and there are trees growing in one straight line
A lot of people are sitting on the rocks. They mostly sit in pairs. Behind them there is a park with trees, and a city skyline.
Inside the studio, we see a drummer practicing on his set. There are multiple drums in the other corners of the room.
The gun shop. There is a man in a cap who is polishing his gun, looking at it, and assembling. There are rows of riffles behind him, on display.

During a fitness practice in the gym, there are 5 women with a barbell on their shoulders, performing squats. The gym is bright inside, with one big circular light source in the centre. After squats, they start doing Bulgarian split squats with the same barbell.

There is a large living room, and a big blue couch sits in the center, where a woman is seated. Near her, there is a baby on a pillow. She feeds the baby from a bottle. We see a dining table behind them.
A panoramic view. There is a big white ledge made out of concrete and tiles. In the left corner, there is a tower with four columns. It is brown.

Train station, while one train departs. People leave with suitcases rolling behind them. It is sunny and bright outside. In the centre, there is a staircase that leads underground, and some people go there. At the end, a man is passing by with a trolley.
Dark bathroom with candles. One candle is on top of a sink, twinkling in the wind. The other is next to it.
Outside in winter, there is a person shoveling snow from their car. It is a street with houses 2-3 stories. There are a lot of other cars along the street as well
There is a corridor that resembles a prison cell with barrs in each room. Inside of a small room there is a dog who plays with the rug on the floor. It wiggles it's tail.

It is a beach in the morning, with the sun high up in the sky. The sea is light blue, with the waves along the shore. The sand is white. There are some people closer to the water. There are also beach houses further behind the fence that divides the beach from the grass.
A person is playing the piano, next to the open window with a view of the city. It is dark outside, and the houses have light in their windows. There is another piano as well, put nobody plays it.

It is a veterinary office with white tiles on the walls. There are kittens inside the small units, going around from side to side. The cats are white with black marks on them. To the right, there are two sinks and kitchen-like cabinets at top. One cat tries to escape its little chamber, so it climbs up the wall inside it.

It is a veterinary office with white tiles on the walls. There are kittens inside the small units, going around from side to side. The cats are white with black marks on them. To the right, there are two sinks and kitchen-like cabinets at top. One cat tries to escape its little chamber, so it climbs up the wall inside it.

In the countryside of the chicken farm. Multiple hens are going around in the grassfield. Behind them there is a barn with a poster that says Freeland. Chickens go around, flying and tasting the grass. The weather is cloudy and the trees behind do not have any leaves on them.

Busy square in the city. There are advertisements on the glass buildings. There is a woman in the centre, she tries to take a picture. She does a pose of her hands up in the air, and the photographer suggests her to try another angle. She goes to the other corner. Meanwhile, a lot of people cross the street, cars go around.
Barber's office. One man does a haircut on the other. He trims his hair. There are only two of them in the shop, but there are multiple empty chairs.
The ambulance car. There is a patient and a nurse checking his vitals on the screen. The patient is covered with blankets and has an oxygen mask on his face. She writes something down on the paper.
Inside of the pig farm. There are many small pigs running around and feeding from separate containers filled with food. The containers have blue lids. Each enclosure consists of a small green fence.

Inside of a museum exhibition. The exhibition is dark to resemble a night with a bright northern light picture. There are figures of animals such as bears, moose, and fish. There are also figures of people dressed in fur, covered head to toe. There is also one real human who stands and looks at one part of an exhibition with a wolf in it.

There is a person inside a shooting range, sitting and aiming at the target with a gun. He is wearing headphones and glasses. The shooting range has three seats and is not very big. Behind a man, there is a wall with a fire extinguisher and a table.

In a city. A double-decker bus of red color comes to a stop and picks up people. Behind a bus, on a square, there is a big white building in a classical style. On the right side of the bus stop, there is a fountain.

In a city. A double-decker bus of red color comes to a stop and picks up people. Behind a bus, on a square, there is a big white building in a classical style. On the right side of the bus stop, there is a fountain.
Inside of a preson cell. There is a bed, a wardrobe and a table with chair and a toilet. On top of the bed there is a small window with the bars on it.

In a grass field. There is a landing place for the helicopter. The helicopter slowly approaches the ground. It is yellow. There is a warehouse in the back. There are also yellow tall boxes made out of profiled sheets.
Inside of a small bedroom. Three men are laughing really hard. They clap and slap in excitement. One of them leans on the wall.

There is a bathroom, with a silver toilet and made of white tile walls with a blue strip of tiles. There is a white garbage bin that's half full. There are three toilet paper rolls, one roll is hanging out ready to be used. The blue tiles are in a pattern of light blue and dark blue. The entrance for the washroom is a large silver door. The bathroom is clean.

The room is covered with gas dials and large spigots on the ceiling, there are wires and cables all over the room. There are gadgets and buttons with black covers on the wall. From top to bottom there are buttons, and handles. There are silver small railings to hold. The floor is painted white and the paint is chipping. There is a small red ramp, and next to that there is a small metal staircase leading to another room. The room is well lit. There is red writing on some of the gas dials, there is a grey and red box on one corner.

This scene shows an empty cafe or restaurant, the chairs are empty, the chairs are coloured in grey and orange and the tables are white with plants and grey dining table covers. There are white pillars around the restaurant area. There are black chandeliers made of four candles hanging from the ceiling. There are green and grey booths on the wall. The room is surrounded by floor to ceiling mirrors, the mirrors are covered by see through curtains and cars pass on the busy road.

In this room there is a floating bed with a man sitting on it, a small reading desk with a black chair, the desk as a remote and other items like a small plant. The curtains are seen through, some of them are open letting in light. There is a small side shelf floating next to the bed. A man wearing a plaid shirt and blue jeans has his legs crossed and is lying on his back on the head of the bed . The man is using his phone and he puts his phone next to the side shelf, he takes a few steps out of his bed and grabs a remote. He turns the TV on standing and sits back down on the bed. The TV is small and mounted across the bed.

This scene shows a bloodied bathroom that has a laundry washer. The washer has a bloodied axe and an organ. There is a walk-in shower with white curtains that are covered in blood stains. The bathroom is made of white tiles that are covered in bloodied hand prints and the text “RUN” on top the bathroom tiles there is a framed rectangular picture of a speed boat. There are red towels on the floor and next to the sink. The sink has a mirror cabinet that has blood stains. The white porcelain sink has more blood going down the drain. There is a black box on the floor, next to the box there is a heater. The toilet is white but has some blood covered and the seat is closed.

This scene is of a bird housing shed. The shed is made of cedar wood planks, there is a large window and an open door entrance. There is a wooden white shelf on one of the walls. The shelves had some toys and slits in them. On the floor there is a yellow bucket, a stool and wooden square planks on the corner. The floor has a silver feeding trout. The birds are sitting on wooden triangles mounted on the wall. They fly down and eat from the feeding trout. They pick at it for a bit and fly back up

The room is small, painted in a light yellow colour with thick cable wires mounted to the tops of the walls lining the room and ceiling, the wires are held together by small metal pieces. The wall has a corded phone hung, there is a small black box that has a button to open a door adjacent to the button. Across from this wall, there is a rectangular light mounted on the wall. On this second wall there is another large metal door. The door slowly opens and a man in a hazmat suite enters the room. The door closes behind him. He walks to the second door and presses the button to open the door. He takes a step back and waits for the door to open

This scene shows a hilly forest with a trail going down a hill leading to a windy pathway. The trees are dead, and a lot of leaves cover the floor. There are patches of snow on the ground, the forest has indented ground patches and the snow covers these areas. The sky is sunny. The wind blows against the branches of the dead trees.

There is a busy fire station, with large red bay doors. The station has four doors, two of them are closed while the other two are open. Two vehicles are reversing into the bay doors. One of them is a smaller ambulance that is red with a bright yellow strip. The other is a large red fire truck with silver side sliding doors and a hose at the back of the truck. Their reverse lights are blinking as they slowly back up into the station. Next to the station there is a neighbourhood of condos. The neighborhood is quiet with no driving cars or people. The pavement is wet, the leaves fell off the trees and the sky is gloomy.

This scene is a soccer field busy with people playing and watching the game. A few of them are sitting on chairs watching while most stand around. Some are sitting far on the wired fence that is surrounding the field. The field is a bit patchy. There are two teams playing, an orange team and yellow team wearing coloured pinnies. The ball is kicked in the air from a distant player and players from the teams rush to grab the ball, two players run into each other and one fouls the other. The ref blows his whistle, the player in yellow helps the orange player on the floor and pats his shoulder. The injured players get up and rejoin the match. The ball is brought back and another player does a free kick.

The scene is looking at a small town from a building with metal scaffolding, there is a green mesh surrounding the scaffolding. The building diminished. The town is made up of houses with large pointy triangular roofs, in the center of the town there is a large building with a lawn surrounding the building, this building has white and black metal and stone fencing, there are some large trees planted and there is a drive way that is open leading to the house. Next to this house there are a lot of other houses with similar designs. The road is clear and one car is parked there.
(missing)

A lady is spray painting the side of a building. The building looks abandoned with broken glass and vines growing on the side of the building. There is a lot of garbage next to the building like loose cement bricks, white bucket squares filled with grass, tires and other small items. Behind one of the large white squares on the ground there is a man wearing a black hoodie looking around. The lady is painting over a white gerifiti mark, the gerifiti is on a silver large door of the building. She moves her body around and takes a second and stops looking at the paint job as she continues to spray the paint.

This scene is a long tunnel, it has a narrow comment pathway big enough for a bike to go down. On the edges there is a small sidewalk on both sides of the path, there is a yellow paint trip separating the sidewalk from the bike path. The tunnel is well lit with walls made of half tile and metal heaters attached to the wall. There are vents mounted on the wall. A man drives down the pathway on his bike, the bike has one light on. Behind there are two people walking. The tiles are coloured white, there is a blue strip of pain at the top half of the tiles, and orange paint on the ceiling.

This scene is a dance hall, in the center there is a dance group, performing hip-hop dance moves as a group. They wear matching outfits and perform in a large open room, there is a large crowd of people sitting down watching them. The stage and dance area is lit with flashing disco lights and blue and pink lights. There is a stage area with a large LED sign that says “hull”. The crowd is cheering and some are clapping for the dancers.

This scene is an underpass tunnel area that is dark which leads to an open field with trees and bushes. The sun has set and there is little light in the sky. A man is riding his bike down this path, a lady passes him but a man rushes at her from the dark shadows of the underpass and he takes her. The lady attempts to resist and screams but the man drags her into the corner.

There is a trail that comes from an open field, and leads to an area that is covered by tall dead trees, the floor is covered in leaves but the pathway is clear.
